----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A very very simple PHP framework to use the Scoop.it API.
	Links:
		- Scoop.it Developers Home : http://www.scoop.it/dev
		- Scoop.it API Talk : http://groups.google.com/group/scoopit-api-talk
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------


INSTRUCTIONS

Please, follow the instructions bellow:

 - Install php5-curl
 - Copy/paste config.php.sample into config.php with your values.  
 - Enjoy, and make your comments!